  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ 425°F/ Gas 7</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add the <strong>macaroni</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook for 7 min or until it's cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the macaroni, reserving 150ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/easy-truffle-mac-n-cheese/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the macaroni is cooking, grate the<strong> cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/easy-truffle-mac-n-cheese/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>grated</strong> <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong> to a bowl with the<strong> panko breadcrumbs</strong> and 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season with a good grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and give it a good mix up – these are your <strong>cheesy breadcrumbs</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/easy-truffle-mac-n-cheese/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve the <strong>Knorr vegetable stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in the <strong>reserved pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/easy-truffle-mac-n-cheese/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>drained macaroni</strong> to the pot with the <strong>crème fraîche</strong>, <strong>truffle flavoured oil</strong>,<strong> vegetable stock</strong>, <strong>grated cheddar cheese</strong> and <strong>Dijon mustard</strong> and give everything a good mix up until fully combined – this is your <strong>truffle mac 'n' cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/easy-truffle-mac-n-cheese/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>truffle mac 'n' cheese</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>and top with the <strong>cheesy breadcrumbs</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 15-20 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/easy-truffle-mac-n-cheese/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the<strong> balsamic vinegar</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> – this is your<strong> dressing</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half and add them to the <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Once the truffle mac 'n' cheese is done, add the<strong> seasonal salad</strong> to the <strong>dressing</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>tomato salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/easy-truffle-mac-n-cheese/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>truffle mac 'n' cheese</strong> with the<strong> tomato salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
  ],
